O

ObservableCayleyColorGraphBuilder<G extends api.Group<G>> - Class in cayleygraphs
This class provides capabilities similar to those of the CayleyGraphBuilder, but with two additional features, namely (i) allowing for external progress listeners that receive updates on the construction process, and (ii) the ability to terminate the construction process.
